jñānavān sattvasaṃpannaḥ sākṣād indra ivāparaḥ / HV_App.I,31.840 /
gandharva iva gāyaṃs tu siddhaḥ siddha iva svayam // HV_App.I,31.841 //
sākṣāt spṛṣṭaṃ tadā viṣṇoḥ kareṇa mṛdupūrvakam / HV_App.I,31.842 /
