adyāpi naiva munayo labhante tādṛśaṃ vapuḥ / HV_App.I,31.844 /
kṛtvā subahuśo ghoraṃ tapaḥ paramaduścaram // HV_App.I,31.845 //
yac ca labdhaṃ tadā tena piśācena nṛpottama / HV_App.I,31.846 /
