tasmin praviṣṭe 'tha samudratoyaṃ @ HV_App.I,31.3435 @
   prajāpatau viśvamukhe jagadgurau | HV_App.I,31.3436 |
nakṣatranāthaḥ samupājagāma @ HV_App.I,31.3437 @
